# 🛒 MERN E-Commerce Platform

This is a full-stack e-commerce web application built using the MERN Stack. The main highlight of this project is the Image-Based Product Search feature, which allows users to upload an image and find relevant products.

## Features

- User Authentication (JWT)
- Product Management
- Image-Based Product Search
- Shopping Cart Functionality
- Order Management
- Responsive UI

## Tech Stack

Frontend: React.js, CSS, Axios
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Database: MongoDB
Authentication: JWT, bcrypt

## What I Learned

- Building REST APIs with Express.js
- MongoDB database design and integration
- JWT Authentication and Authorization
- Frontend-Backend communication using Axios
- Deploying full-stack applications